videos.description: Trevon Duval steps in front of Anas Mahmoud's pass and goes the other way for the transition slam.
videos.headline: Mahmoud's turnover springs Duval's jam for Duke

videos.description: Duke recognizes longtime play-by-play announcer Mike Patrick who retired from ESPN.
videos.headline: Duke honors Mike Patrick

videos.description: Grayson Allen is off the mark on his shot, but Javin DeLaurier flies in for the Duke dunk.
videos.headline: DeLaurier finishes with a putback jam for Duke

videos.description: Trevon Duval threads one in to Javin DeLaurier, who sends the ball to Marques Bolden for the easy Duke dunk.
videos.headline: Duke's precise passing sets up Bolden's jam

videos.description: Grayson Allen finds Wendell Carter Jr., who makes the extra pass to Marques Bolden for the easy flush.
videos.headline: Bolden rewarded by Duke's pick-and-roll passing

videos.description: Duke continues to dominate Louisville as Alex O'Connell finds Wendell Carter Jr. for another dunk.
videos.headline: Carter makes his presence felt with another Duke slam

videos.description: Grayson Allen picks off an inbounds pass and goes the other way for the jam. Trevon Duval picks up a loose ball on the next possession and leads Gary Trent Jr. for another dunk.
videos.headline: Allen, Trent get easy dunks off Louisville turnovers

videos.description: Wendell Carter Jr. videobombs Grayson Allen's post-game interview before Allen mentions how the Blue Devils have been clicking of late.
videos.headline: Carter invades Allen's interview
